data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This stunning 4-bedroom, 2.5-bath beauty is a perfect blend of elegance and comfort. Picture yourself in the heart of this home, where granite countertops and tile flooring adorn the living spaces, giving a touch of luxury to everyday living. Indulge in the spaciousness of each bedroom, all equipped with walk-in closets, ensuring ample storage for your lifestyle. The master bedroom, complete with its expansive walk-in closet, is your personal sanctuary within this haven of tranquility. Practicality meets style with a convenient two-car garage, providing both shelter for your vehicles and additional storage space. But what truly sets this home apart is its prime location-nestled against a lush green belt, you'll enjoy unrivaled privacy with no neighbors behind you. Don't just imagine your ideal lifestyle; experience it. Schedule a showing today, and let this home speak to you. Your future home awaits! This home is also available through owner finance. Seller is willing to help with up to 10k to buy rate down.
